{"sn10.5:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 10.5 ","sn10.5:0.2":"1. Indakavagga ","sn10.5:0.3":"Sanusutta ","sn10.5:1.1":"Ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame. ","sn10.5:1.2":"Tena kho pana samayena annatarissa upasikaya sanu nama putto yakkhena gahito hoti. ","sn10.5:1.3":"Atha kho sa upasika paridevamana tayam velayam ima gathayo abhasi: ","sn10.5:2.1":"“Catuddasim pancadasim, ","sn10.5:2.2":"ya ca pakkhassa atthami; ","sn10.5:2.3":"Patihariyapakkhanca, ","sn10.5:2.4":"atthangasusamagatam. ","sn10.5:3.1":"Uposatham upavasanti, ","sn10.5:3.2":"brahmacariyam caranti ye; ","sn10.5:3.3":"Na tehi yakkha kilanti, ","sn10.5:3.4":"iti me arahatam sutam; ","sn10.5:3.5":"Sa dani ajja passami, ","sn10.5:3.6":"yakkha kilanti sanuna”ti. ","sn10.5:4.1":"“Catuddasim pancadasim, ","sn10.5:4.2":"ya ca pakkhassa atthami; ","sn10.5:4.3":"Patihariyapakkhanca, ","sn10.5:4.4":"atthangasusamagatam; ","sn10.5:5.1":"Uposatham upavasanti, ","sn10.5:5.2":"brahmacariyam caranti ye. ","sn10.5:5.3":"Na tehi yakkha kilanti, ","sn10.5:5.4":"sahu te arahatam sutam; ","sn10.5:6.1":"Sanum pabuddham vajjasi, ","sn10.5:6.2":"yakkhanam vacanam idam; ","sn10.5:6.3":"Makasi papakam kammam, ","sn10.5:6.4":"avi va yadi va raho. ","sn10.5:7.1":"Sace ca papakam kammam, ","sn10.5:7.2":"karissasi karosi va; ","sn10.5:7.3":"Na te dukkha pamutyatthi, ","sn10.5:7.4":"uppaccapi palayato”ti. ","sn10.5:8.1":"“Matam va amma rodanti, ","sn10.5:8.2":"yo va jivam na dissati; ","sn10.5:8.3":"Jivantam amma passanti, ","sn10.5:8.4":"kasma mam amma rodasi”ti. ","sn10.5:9.1":"“Matam va putta rodanti, ","sn10.5:9.2":"yo va jivam na dissati; ","sn10.5:9.3":"Yo ca kame cajitvana, ","sn10.5:9.4":"punaragacchate idha; ","sn10.5:9.5":"Tam vapi putta rodanti, ","sn10.5:9.6":"puna jivam mato hi so. ","sn10.5:10.1":"Kukkula ubbhato tata, ","sn10.5:10.2":"kukkulam patitumicchasi; ","sn10.5:10.3":"Naraka ubbhato tata, ","sn10.5:10.4":"narakam patitumicchasi. ","sn10.5:11.1":"Abhidhavatha bhaddante, ","sn10.5:11.2":"kassa ujjhapayamase; ","sn10.5:11.3":"Aditta nihatam bhandam, ","sn10.5:11.4":"puna dayhitumicchasi”ti. "}